   ___|---==°°°Release Notes°°°==---------------------------------------|___ 
      |                                                                 |
        After we found out, that the releases of Accession can’t 
        be burned *Selfbooting*, cause the IP.BIN was missing on their 
        releases and the 1ST_READ.BIN seemed to be modified we decided
        to release these two files as *Selfbooting Patch*. With these 
        two files you can make the games Selfbooting, like it was 
        explained in the SelfBoot TUTORIAL from ECHELON, so here 
        comes the first one, its for Snow Surfers (remember that you 
        will get Rippin Riders, the US version of Snow Surfers after 
        fixing the game with our fix).

