   ___|---==°°°Game Info°°°==-------------------------------------------|___ 
      |                                                                 |
        "Sega and UEP systems bring you Snow Surfers to the Dreamcast. 
        An exhilarating and breathtaking experience that emulates the 
        feeling of rushing down a mountain. Race against the clock, 
        pull off the most amazing tricks or just admire the beautiful 
        scenery as you aim for the ultimate snowboarding goal. Snow 
        Surfers - hang onto your armchair this is going to be a wild 
        Ride!”
       
-	Game Features: 

        Supports Vibration Pack and Visual Memory 
        1-2 Players. 
        Works with RGB/SCART cable 
        VGA adaptor NOT supported.                              

